---
title: Pork and Caramelised Onion Sausages with Celeriac Colcannon and Apple Chutney Gravy
description: There’s no beating the classic combination of bangers and mash. Chef Andre has created a deliciously creamy, pillowy Colcannon using celeriac, which lends the side a nutty overtone. Drizzled in an apple chutney gravy, this dish is sweet, rich with flavour and full of hearty goodness perfect for the colder nights.
